# SOURCES VERIFIED

• arXiv:2512.23325v1 (Ghose, Dec 2025): "Quantum Rashomon Effect as Failure of Gluing"
  - Confirms: Wigner = gluing obstruction = Čech H¹
  - Does NOT define Δ or H⁰ restricted to classical content

• arXiv:1102.0264 / New J. Phys. 13, 113036 (Abramsky-Brandenburger, 2011)
  - Foundational paper on sheaf-theoretic contextuality
  - Defines global sections, contextuality hierarchy
  - Does NOT define what survives when sections don't exist

• arXiv:1408.0049: Categories of Quantum and Classical Channels
  - Instruments in CP*/discard setting

